message.content:
You are a senior TypeScript/React Native reviewer. Deeply review these catch block changes for a lint fix PR.

## Context
The project is a React Native microfrontend (Reward Program). These catch blocks exist in service/hook files that use Zustand for state management.

## File 1: src/services/hooks/useAirlineMiles.ts
```typescript
// BEFORE (line 27):
} catch (error) {
  airlineMilesActions.setError('Failed to load airline miles marketplace');
  return false;
}

// AFTER:
} catch (_error) {
  airlineMilesActions.setError('Failed to load airline miles marketplace');
  return false;
}
```

## File 2: src/services/services/marketplace.service.ts
```typescript
// BEFORE (line 28):
} catch (error) {
  marketplaceActions.setError('Erro ao carregar marketplace');
  marketplaceActions.setStatus(MarketplaceStatus.ERROR);
}

// AFTER:
} catch (_error) {
  marketplaceActions.setError('Erro ao carregar marketplace');
  marketplaceActions.setStatus(MarketplaceStatus.ERROR);
}
```

